			</div>
			<div style="padding: 15px;">
				<img src="images/service-2.jpg" alt="Service 2" height="400" weight="500">
				<h3>Free Wi-Fi</h3>
				<p>All of our rooms come with free high-speed Wi-Fi.</p>
